			<small class="commentmetadata"><a href="#comment-268" title="">November 4th, 2006 at 5:54 pm</a> </small>

			<p>Frank: What&#8217;s up with the bird themed names? Have you been watching National Geographic all day? <img src='http://blog.james-carr.org/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif' alt=';)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>
