<p>Old and Busted: Test Driven Development.<br />
The new hotness: Test Driven Unit Testing.</p>
<p>I have yet to see a unit test for a unit test yet, however. <img src='http://blog.james-carr.org/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_sad.gif' alt=':(' class='wp-smiley' /></p>

