			<p>Good work James. I&#8217;ll be interested in seeing the final article and the pattern descriptions. You have an important set of principles captured here. As is typically the case at this stage of development, the current list may be lacking in orthogonality, but I&#8217;m sure that will get fleshed out.</p>
