			<p>Wonderful post! I&#8217;m glad it&#8217;s resurfaced for those of us who missed it the first time around. The Web Surfer and The Nitpicker are two I keep seeing repeatedly, as well as Excessive Setup which I&#8217;ve always thought of as Much Ado About Nothing.</p>
